            <CommunityForm client:load />
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

{/* FAQ Section - Edit0 Style */}
<section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-green-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</h2>
            <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Everything you need to know</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
            <details class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer text-gray-900">What is this community about?</summary>
                <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">A student-led initiative at the University of Lucknow focused on filmmaking, photography, videography, editing, and storytelling. We bring together creative minds to learn, collaborate, and create amazing content.</p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer text-gray-900">Is it really free to join?</summary>
                <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">Yes! This community is completely free for all University of Lucknow students. No hidden fees, no memberships - just pure creativity and collaboration.</p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer text-gray-900">Do I need prior experience?</summary>
                <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">Not at all! Whether you're a complete beginner or an experienced creator, there's a place for you. We offer workshops and mentorship for all skill levels.</p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer text-gray-900">What equipment do I need?</summary>
                <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">Start with what you have - even a smartphone camera works! As the community grows, we'll provide access to shared equipment and resources.</p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer text-gray-900">How much time commitment is required?</summary>
                <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">You decide! Join workshops when you can, participate in projects that interest you, or simply stay connected. Flexibility is key to our community.</p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer text-gray-900">When does this start?</summary>
                <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">We're currently gathering interest! Once we have enough responses, we'll organize our first meet-up and start creating together. Fill out the form to stay updated.</p>
            </details>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

{/* CTA Section */}
<section class="py-24 px-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-emerald-500">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center max-w-3xl">
